message.body: So it's back to muggs again
I thought u said people never talk
Well I'm talking
And it looks like you are not
I slept in!
Webfoot!
I woke up at six and fell back to sleep around nine and now I'm sweaty and fuzzy headed
Woah I fell asleep at 4 yesterday and slept till 8 today
Now I am really sore and hungry
Oh wow. That is crazy
Do you feel sick?
How did the kiddo let you sleep so late
No sick but achey
I gotta stretch a lot I think
I woke up with her at six, and felt like I couldn't sleep any more. Then we put on more ren and stimpy and I passed out
I think you need to stretch more, yes
Stretching everyday
I also need better chair to work in so I don't cramp up
Yes, not a dumpster chair. You should take stretch breaks while you work too
I want to but I feel like I won't get enough work done
I feel like new sneakers would help out too.
My current pair are worn through
You are such a hard worker. Just a few minutes to stretch your bAck the other way.
I feel like I'm already working at a disadvantage and don't want to make it worse
Oh no. You need support from the ground up!
I'm getting food cuz I didn't eat today
Well yeah, you should be doing everything you can to no exasperate the situation
And you need to eat every day
I'm cutting out coffee starting today
I'm getting an egg and cheese hoagie
I think I need to drink more water
Oh boy.
I didn't drink any coffee today either
I like to add grilled onion and hotsauce
Yes, probably. I've been trying to drink my recommended amount
Half your weight in ounces I think
I don't drink nearly that much
Yeah, it's kind of a lot. Plus you should drink a glass of water for every cup of coffee you drink, ontop of that amount
I can aim for half that amount
I mean anything is better than nearly nothing
What is your plan 4 today
Going to school to pick up my paycheck, then going for a hike of some sort, maybe one that ends with a water spot
That's sounds fun
I'd like to go to the blue lake, but it seems a little scary with just the two of us
What about the pools they are open
It's really hot today
Hmm maybe.
Pools are so gross tho
Yeah but there are not fish and game wardens
Fish versus band aids is a tough call
Not the fish it's the tickets
You only have to worry about tickets there on the weekends. But I don't want to drive out there
So what r u gona do
It's raining and about five degrees cooler in Bryn Mawr so we are just enjoying rain walks. Going to get lunch in a minute
Ok I'm just working at home and having a bad day
Oh no, what can I do for you?
Get me a job
While I'm at Bryn Mawr I will find you one.
Ok thanks
Can I bring you anything?
No I have to go shopping soon I have no food
Ok. I think I have a uti..very uncomfortable
Oh boy make a dr apt ASAP
Uhhhh
You have health insurance so take advantage of it while you have it
Yeah, I'm having a problem with my ins tho, I need to call them
Get it sorted.
I need an assistant
You are an assistant.
I need to start life over
You are telling me
I got mess, feeling better already. Are you still regretting your existence?
Mess-->meds
You saw the dr already
I am still pretty bummed yeah
I just got an rx over the phone. I'm sorry you are bummed. I wish there were something I could do
I can't think of what would help
A rich girlfriend with a rooftop pool and a French villa.
You're right, that would probably help a little.
Like a rooftop pool here or a rooftop pool in the French villa?
Because I don't really need the pool in France. I'd be in the Mediterranean.
Here it would be a roof top pool, in France it would be the kind of pool that goes to an edge and overlooks a valley
Her parents would be art dealers too
Rich people like to have superfluous pools
I would rather they weren't interested in art at all because then I would have to talk about it all the time
But then they could create an international interest in it, and you could spend your days as you please
I would rather be ignored by them and just use the villa when they aren't there. That's more than any art career would ever get me.
Ok, they don't even know you exist.
That would be best, just use their stuff and funds while they are busy pillaging the world. I'm a good caretaker, they probably would pay me to watch their stuff.

They can't pay you if they don't know you exist. She could probably have you written into some sort of payroll. You are a secret because they don't wanther dating until she is finished with college...and she still has two more years!
They are so naive to think she won't date in college. They are just living in denial, which I guess most of the very rich are.
She's always been very strong willed, and they only accept her deception because it is easier than confrontation.
No it's because they don't really know her because she was raised by nannys and boarding school tutors. She just wants the person that lovers her to actu
ally pay attention to her.
Because people have only ever loved her for her incredible physical beauty, and not who she is on the inside.
She's not that beautiful.
Whatever
The light coming in the window is so golden
You know the old sailing limerick... Yellow sky at dusk ... sailors combust .
There is a rainbow behind my house.
I knew there would be one
I ate steamed cabbage with garlic because I had no food.
But had cabbage in the garden.
I thought you were going out to get food! We would've invited you over
Or we could have gone out
That's what gardens are for
I am working and couldn't come over anyways
Oh boy.
This hasn't really been my day , or week or life.
I think those are the lyrics to the friends theme song
Baby, you need to stop shitting on your life. It's not healthy or productive. And it makes your girl friend feel inadequate
Oh great I'm getting older and more banal too
You like drinking cappuccinos
No it's just been tough its not your fault.
So did you deposit your sweet sweet Bryn Mwar cash
Not yet, just picked it up. I'm glad I don't have to pay rent in July, but I'm stressed about finding a new place
Yeah it's scary but it will be an opportunity to get more space for you and smells
Smella
It will be good. It will be nice to have a room mate in a really similar situation as me
Yeah I bet it will be more important to have a friend that understands what it's like to be a single mom than have more space.
Do you think it will get crazy with two kids in the house?
Yeah, a single mom in school too.
It might be crazy at times, but I'm hoping that it will help Ella with maturity..seeing how a toddler acts and not wanting to act like a baby
Yah u don't wana get out behaved by a toddler when you are nine
Yeah, not cool.
She will get to see what it sounds like when someone else is whining
Pretty annoying
It's strange for me to think that she doesn't realize things like that because I haven't seen her development from a young age.
Like that statement about how she just realized you did things when she wasn't with you.
Yeah. I think she is easier to appreciate when you get the big picture
Not that she is unappreciated but that I am unaccustomed to child development
Speaking of behavior. I watched the South Park episode about the dog whisperer last night, it was so great!
You never saw that one?
Cartman finally gets out on his place
Put in
No I didn't even know it existed! I like that it was called tsst!
On the neck
That's how you control even the worse kid
I can't believe that those kids are supposed to be 8 or 9
I thought they were in fourth and fifth grade?
Single mothers ruin their children because they are lonely and rejected
Maybe 4 th grade
I think if you just love the kid they will be ok.
And don't steal from them
And don't abuse them while they are recovering from a traumatic brain injury
You get too hard on yourself as a mom
You are doing a great job with Ella
She says she loves you all the time.
I almost never said that to my parents when I was a kid.
But I also didn't spend that much time with my parents.
You also have to undo all of her dads anti-parenting
A one word book report? Come on
No that's how the episode ended. Cartmans mom asked Caesar out, and when he said no, she conditioned cartmen into his old ways
Thanks though for all of the kind words.
I hAve to rewatch the episode
Right? It's like he encourages her to not care by not caring
It's good. He doesn't mention bad woman energy tho
It should have brought that up
Yeah it's best to avoid his level
I love when Eric freaks out on his walk with Cesar and he's on a leash
Oh my I am so sore.
Oh no. You need a real bed
Calm submissive energy
I need a new body
Are you stretching before you start?
Start what
No probably not
Sometimes
Start work
Tomorrow we will stretch in the am
I had so many nightmares
You always have nightmares like its a contest to have the most
